      <title>特朗普说，印度不会避免在4月2日受到关税的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-india-will-be-hit-by-reciprocal-tariffs-on-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，即使在新德里·斯库里（New Delhi Scurry）的官员通过减少贸易障碍来安抚华盛顿的官员，印度将受到类似的职责袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-india-will-be-hit-by-reciprocal-tariffs-on-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 05:36:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南现在允许一些国内银行的外国所有权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/vietnam-now-allows-49-foreign-ownership-of-some-domestic-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南政府允许少数银行的外国所有权；从30％＆mdash提高；这已经接管了苦苦挣扎的金融机构，以加快央行重组陷入困境的贷方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/vietnam-now-allows-49-foreign-ownership-of-some-domestic-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 05:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙（Macron）正在与特朗普（Trump）发生冲突，以帮助乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/russia-ukraine-trump-macron-heading-for-clash-with-trump-over-ukraine-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）与他的地缘政治演习震撼了我们的盟友时，这种情况帮助一位欧洲领导人重返焦点：伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/russia-ukraine-trump-macron-heading-for-clash-with-trump-over-ukraine-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟领导人要努力应对特朗普的俄罗斯甘比特：看什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/eu-leaders-to-grapple-with-trump-s-russia-gambit-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟领导人将旨在确认他们在周四举行的峰会上加强国防支出的计划，但现在面临更加紧迫的关注：他们是否将在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在乌克兰快速停火的努力中发挥作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/eu-leaders-to-grapple-with-trump-s-russia-gambit-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚总统计划命名Ávila下一任财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/colombia-s-president-plans-to-name-avila-next-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）接近命名该国国营银行集团负责人Germánávila作为他的下一任财政部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/colombia-s-president-plans-to-name-avila-next-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 04:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼立法者在政府中发挥了更大的作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/indonesia-passes-law-allowing-bigger-military-role-in-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚周四通过了立法，扩大了东南亚最大的武装部队的作用，在苏哈托独裁统治并在普拉博沃·苏贝安托（Prabowo Subianto）总统的领导下提出了有关该国指导的新问题，撤消了二十年前安装的一些路缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/indonesia-passes-law-allowing-bigger-military-role-in-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 03:34:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国的婚姻跳跃，为衰老国家提供了希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/south-korea-s-marriages-jump-offering-hopes-for-aging-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国婚姻在一个充满希望的迹象中提高了韩国婚姻，这是一个充满希望的迹象，而这个国家一直在加大努力，以提高世界上最低的生育率，这是经济上悲观情绪的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/south-korea-s-marriages-jump-offering-hopes-for-aging-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率，因为关税会加热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美联储应降低利率，并随着官员的关税推动而权衡的经济成本而与美国中央银行分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普着手签署行政命令拆除教育部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-set-to-sign-executive-order-eliminating-education-department</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）有望签署一项行政诉讼，要求官员采取措施拆除教育部，这是他为减少联邦政府及其劳动力规模的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-set-to-sign-executive-order-eliminating-education-department</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 22:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列部队在加沙地带开始有限的地面入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/israeli-forces-begin-limited-ground-operation-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列说，它于周三在加沙开始了有限的地面行动，除非哈马斯释放其剩余59人的人质，否则部队返回人口中心以外的某些职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/israeli-forces-begin-limited-ground-operation-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 15:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
